FBIS3-54802 "drsov002_r_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 Azerbaijan Iran, Turkey, Azerbaijan To Make Joint Appeal NC0301195694 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network in Azeri 1600 GMT 3 Jan 94 NC0301195694 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network Language: Azeri Article Type:BFN [Text] It was agreed during Foreign Minister Gasan Gasanov recent visit to Iran and Turkey that Azerbaijan, Turkey, and Iran will jointly appeal to the Islamic Conference Organization to send a commission to confirm the destruction of the religious, cultural, and historic monuments by the Armenian Armed Forces in the lands it has occupied.
